xfce4-claude-status-plugin (0.2.0-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Rewrite core logic in Rust with C FFI wrapper
  * Move credential loading, API client, transcript parsing to Rust
  * Add file monitoring for credentials changes using notify crate
  * Remove json-glib and libsoup dependencies (now handled by Rust)
  * Improve error handling and code organization

